<div class="extratitle">RPC Ping</div>

<p>Use this function to announce your blog to some popular rpc blog services.
Your blog along with a link to it will then appear on their frontpages, which
enables people to find your blog.
</p>
<p>
<a href="{$config.whoami}?admin=yes&mode=admin_rpcping">Execute RPC ping now</a>
</p>
<p>You may
<a href="{$config.whoami}?admin=yes&mode=admin_config_edit&configfile=admin-options.conf&back=admin_extras">edit the options file</a>,
which contains a list to a couple of rpc ping sites. Add or remove some as you like.</p>
